{
  "stem": "27509.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you had to utilize the time to make up for the slowness of the-- the production.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had day shift and night shift.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On Friday night when there was no activity in the factory, when-- when it was quiet, absolutely quiet, it was hard to sleep because we missed the music of the going machines.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who was employed?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all Jewish people were employed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of them stands out in particular in my memory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a well built man with a beard, with the Hassidic cap, who was very outspoken about politics.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And although he was a religious Jew, in terms of his political orientation he was a communist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so there is no-- that-- not to be-- not to be amazed at such a juxtaposition of religious orientation and political, almost counter-ideology.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was-- that was part of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, in the second room there was the overlocker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the dining room was an open shop door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So people are coming and going all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes it was quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes there were more than one person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if you would consider the fact that in the olden days, to find the appropriate garment was in itself a major decision.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you have to add in terms of sociological interaction the fact that after they have picked the garment and asked for the price, they started bargaining because it wasn't the case that you-- and in our-- our place, my father has introduced the rule that there was no bargaining.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He would not-- he quoted a price and you would not budge.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
